	(md_parse_option): Handle OPTION_INSN32 and OPTION_NO_INSN32.
	(s_mipsset): Handle "insn32" and "noinsn32" pseudo-ops.
	(mips_handle_align): Handle insn32 mode.
	(md_show_usage): Add -minsn32 and -mno-insn32.

